Do you have a party, company event, sporting event or celebration to plan this summer or fall?! Schedule your Airbrush Face Painting & Temporary Tattoo Services with Arlene's Costumes Airbrush face painting and temporary tattoos build enthusiasm for special occasions, teams, families and more.

We have been in business for 69 years and have been doing Airbrush Face Painting and Temporary Tattoos for nearly 30 years!

Our colorful designs stay on for a few days or come off easily with liquid soap or a little rubbing alcohol

We are the official airbrush face painters of the Buffalo Bills, the Rochester Amerks, the Rochester Red Wings and the Lilac Festival.
